{"tid":706361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［無圖］紅燒曱甴","createTime":"2018-06-17T20:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T10:02:35.000Z","uid":176763,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3ad6cf390b3d9d555b10b04b7ac6b7af6e154a","tid":706361,"uid":176763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T20:31:55.000Z","msg":"頭先睇波 賭了亦輸了<br />\n心情十分低落 入廚房想飲杯水舒緩一下<br />\n竟然讓我發現兩隻可惡的曱甴<br />\n二話不說便用手掌打了一下 一隻倒下 再一巴 同伴亦戰敗<br />\n兩隻同時典下典下<br />\n我唯有帶它們參加campfire<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/042739_927323c03e0738fddd51bcda04328416.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F042739_927323c03e0738fddd51bcda04328416.png&h=6d2bbb6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一起火 佢地已經即刻反哂肚 睇得出佢地都好享受！ 你睇！腳都紅埋！<br />\n<br />\n燒咗無耐 好臭窿味 熄火 原封不動 殺一儆百!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b167d97cc5dd676b37d31edb6ae15940deba98dd","tid":706361,"uid":85957,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T20:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/043510_15322527d4197d089026a0b4fe897081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F043510_15322527d4197d089026a0b4fe897081.jpg&h=f1ac7890&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e54addbe96031eb2af862af743bb105501a8c9b","tid":706361,"uid":176763,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b167d97cc5dd676b37d31edb6ae15940deba98dd","tid":706361,"uid":85957,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T20:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/043510_15322527d4197d089026a0b4fe897081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://